<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 15:16:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在欧盟的中国企业表示，在全球紧张局势中，商业环境更加严峻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/business-conditions-tougher-chinese-firms-eu-say-amid-global-tensions-2024-12-09/</link><description>周一公布的一项调查显示，在欧盟的中国企业表示，商业环境连续第五年恶化，地缘政治紧张局势加剧和反华情绪阻碍了运营。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/business-conditions-tougher-chinese-firms-eu-say-amid-global-tensions-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>字节跳动、TikTok 寻求暂时停止美国禁令，等待最高法院审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/bytedance-tiktok-seek-temporary-halt-us-crackdown-law-pending-supreme-court-2024-12-09/</link><description>这些公司警告说，如果没有这项命令，法律将“在总统就职前夕关闭 TikTok——美国最受欢迎的语音平台之一——其每月超过 1.7 亿的国内用户。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:21:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/bytedance-tiktok-seek-temporary-halt-us-crackdown-law-pending-supreme-court-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着需求不断增长，中国小米将于明年夏天推出新款 SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xiaomi-announces-new-suv-launch-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国电子产品制造商小米周一表示，预计将在明年 6 月或 7 月推出首款 SUV YU7，进一步进军中国竞争激烈的汽车市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 12:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xiaomi-announces-new-suv-launch-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>LGIM表示对中国不太乐观；英国后备母猪报价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-lgim-urgent-2024-12-09/</link><description>Legal &amp;amp; General Investment Management 首席投资官索尼娅·劳德 (Sonja Laud) 周一表示，中国仍面临非常困难的经济形势，目前还很难对世界第二大经济体持乐观态度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 12:19:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-lgim-urgent-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国对英伟达展开反垄断调查，美国芯片紧张局势升级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-investigates-nvidia-over-suspected-violation-antimonopoly-law-2024-12-09/</link><description>此次调查是在美国上周对中国半导体行业发起三年来的第三次打压之后进行的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 11:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-investigates-nvidia-over-suspected-violation-antimonopoly-law-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>美洲 美联储降息，中国改变货币立场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-09/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 11:10:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>前俄罗斯 ASML 员工被指控盗窃知识产权和违反制裁行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/former-russian-asml-employee-set-court-hearing-alleged-ip-theft-case-2024-12-09/</link><description>荷兰一家法院周一延长了对半导体设备制造商 ASML 一名俄罗斯前雇员的拘留，该雇员涉嫌窃取知识产权并将其出售给俄罗斯买家，违反了欧洲制裁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:59:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/former-russian-asml-employee-set-court-hearing-alleged-ip-theft-case-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股市因中国刺激乐观情绪而走高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-bounce-china-stimulus-optimism-2024-12-09/</link><description>欧洲股市周一徘徊在六周高点附近，在矿业和奢侈品股的带动下，有迹象表明有新的刺激措施支持中国经济放缓。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:32:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-bounce-china-stimulus-optimism-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国誓言加大政策刺激力度，刺激2025年经济增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-announces-first-monetary-policy-shift-since-2010-spur-growth-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国将采取“适度宽松”的货币政策，这是近14年来首次放松政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:29:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-announces-first-monetary-policy-shift-since-2010-spur-growth-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国监管机构要求银行加快离岸公司上市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-regulators-tell-banks-expedite-offshore-company-listings-sources-say-2024-12-09/</link><description>消息人士称，中国大陆和香港的监管机构已要求一些全球最大的投资银行帮助加快中国企业在香港上市的速度，以促进海外融资并重振世界第二大经济体。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-regulators-tell-banks-expedite-offshore-company-listings-sources-say-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国呼吁“政治解决”以恢复叙利亚稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-calls-political-solution-restore-stability-syria-2024-12-09/</link><description>在叛军周末占领叙利亚首都、叙利亚总统逃往俄罗斯后，中国外交部周一呼吁尽快在叙利亚找到“政治解决方案”，以恢复稳定和秩序。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:48:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-calls-political-solution-restore-stability-syria-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国亿万富翁马云罕见地看到了蚂蚁集团的人工智能未来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-billionaire-jack-ma-sees-ai-future-ant-group-rare-appearance-2024-12-09/</link><description>自中国暂停 2020 年 IPO 计划以来，阿里巴巴联合创始人马云罕见地公开露面，表达了对其子公司蚂蚁集团未来的信心，并看到了这家金融科技巨头在人工智能领域的重大机遇。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-billionaire-jack-ma-sees-ai-future-ant-group-rare-appearance-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着经济刺激措施的实施，中国11月银行贷款预计将翻一番</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-nov-bank-lending-seen-doubling-stimulus-kicks-2024-12-09/</link><description>路透周一的一项民意调查显示，中国11月份新增人民币贷款预计将比10月份增加近一倍，这表明随着北京方面近期支持经济增长的努力提振信心，信贷需求更加坚挺。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 06:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-nov-bank-lending-seen-doubling-stimulus-kicks-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲经济萎靡，领导层空缺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/europes-economic-malaise-add-leadership-void-2024-12-09/</link><description>法国和德国的政治危机使欧洲陷入困境的经济实现现代化的努力遭遇挫折，并且已经使企业更难做出全球竞争所需的投资决策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 06:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/europes-economic-malaise-add-leadership-void-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>市场关注消费者物价指数数据，美元紧张不安；澳元、新西兰元对中国崛起</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/loonie-aussie-focus-while-us-dollar-extends-gains-2024-12-09/</link><description>由于投资者等待本周晚些时候的美国通胀数据，周一欧元兑美元在紧张的交易中保持稳定，而在中国承诺明年“适度宽松”的货币政策后，澳元和新西兰元上涨。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 05:43:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/loonie-aussie-focus-while-us-dollar-extends-gains-2024-12-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>